    "The NNs work as a decoder in the described setting based on the encoded environment state.",
    "Therefore, the control agent consists of an encoder and a decoder.",
    "The encoder is implemented using a graph neural network (GNN).",
    "As a result, a fixed-size vector representing the current simulation state is passed to the encoder.",
    "To prove the RL's applicability to the layout planning and scheduling of LMAS, the environment depicted in Fig. 4 was implemented using a DES."
